Text.string: Ohhh, big mistake, boyo!
Let's have us a donnybrook, then!
You throwin' shapes at me, now?
Right, let's have it!
You're just beggin' for a burial!
The bigger they are, the more I get paid!
Oi, think you're somethin' special, dontcha?
This one's gonna be right murderous!
Big fella, aintcha?
Ah, bugger, we got a badass!
Absolutely lethal!
Getting better all the time!
Meet the new Zane: faster, stronger, even more handsome!
Wait'll they get a load of me…
My standard rate just doubled!
I'm getting' to be pretty first-rate, even if I say so meself!
Just when you thought I couldn't get any better…
Nobody but nobody outshines Zane Flynt!
Ah, Zane, like a fine wine, you are!
Flynt, my boy, you're sharper than ever!
You'll want to think twice next time!
You crossed me and you're dead, fancy that!
Did that one have a bounty? No? You sure?
One assassination, on the house!
Now THAT'S a thing of beauty!
Sorry, were you sayin' somethin?
Sorry about your face, or whatever that was!
Well, that settles it, doesn't it!
Let that be a lesson to ye!
And stay out!
Someone get a mop!
That'll sort ye!
(laughter) Oh, that never gets old.
From the hip! Figuratively.
I'm a one man bloody army!
The lads are gonna love this!
Havin' a blast!
Oh, this is a riot!
Kablooie!
Oo, that's got a bit of kick to it!
It'll take a lot more than that, boyo.
You must've thought you were the grog's bollocks, didn't ya?
Say hello to my brothers for me!
That's it, biggun, you've had your fun!
Your days of badassery are well behind ya!
Shoulder shooter, takin' aim!
Layin' waste!
Watch the birdie!
(loudly) What? Speak up, this thing's right by my ear!
Let's shake things up!
Portable devastation, for the killer on the go!
Now THIS is a shooter!
Look, mam, no hands!
Trick shot!
This'll make a fine mess!
Hold still, this thing's tricky to aim!
That's right, it's… another gun!
This oughta do the trick!
Shoulder cannon, pew, pew!
Shoulder cannon, give us a hand, wouldja?
Need a charge!
Damn, outta juice!
Come on, come on!
You MUST be joking.
WELL, this is embarrassing!
Shoulder shooter's empty!
Cannon's dry!
Shooter's spent!
How the bloody hell do I reload this thing?
Gotta charge me damn cannon!
Damn, I keep dyin' before I get tired. Honestly, I've forgotten what sleep even feels like.
Ah hell, I think I left something back there! Actually, you know what, I'll just get it later.
I'm back! Nobody'd better have touched me things!
Family reunions, always over too soon!
Did I die, or am I just waking up from one of those boring dreams of going to work?

It's probably safe to take a break, I don't SEE anyone about… but that's how they getcha! They sneak up on you when you're just standin' there, and then WHAM, bottle opener through the jugular! At least, that's how I'd kill me. Wait, where's my digi-clone?
When you get to be my age, you learn to appreciate the rare moments of peace and quiet… right, that was nice for a few seconds but now I'm bored again COME ON!

Right, let's have a look at me schedule for the day… kill blokes, check, take their stuff, check, look devilishly handsome, big ol' check… looks like I'm ahead of schedule! Guess I can take a short break. But! Then we're back to killin'!

You know, once you've killed everyone in a room, there's really not that much to do but stand around. Unless you're in a pub, I s'pose. Is there a pub round here? Is this… is this what regular people do for fun?
Am I…? Damn. I think I'm wearing my shirt inside out. No one's said anything--you know, I think I'm pullin' this off! Just play it cool, Zane boy, play it cool.
The only thing that hurts is my pride… and everything else…
Damn, not lookin' forward to the bill…
Ah, damn, I had a line for this…
The Flynt family curse strikes again…
If I could, I'd do it all over again… and probably will.
